        "answer": "The official website for Attijari SICAR is www.attijarisicar.com.tn. Attijari SICAR is a capital investment subsidiary of Attijari Bank. It focuses on financing and investing in Tunisian SMEs.\nAttijari Bank Tunisie is a Tunisian universal bank with 1,001-5,000 employees and operates in banking. It has 86,230 LinkedIn followers. The bank is located in Tunis, Tunisia.\nAttijari Sicar is a subsidiary of Attijariwafa Bank, based in Tunisia. It focuses on investment services. The parent company is Attijariwafa Bank SA, headquartered in Morocco.\nAttijari SICAR is a capital investment arm of Attijari bank, focusing on funding investment programs for businesses. It was formerly part of AngelList, which spun off its jobs service to form Wellfound. Wellfound aims to connect talent with startups.\nAttijari SICAR is a capital investment arm of Attijari Bank, focusing on financing Tunisian SMEs. It is a SICAR, a Luxembourg-based investment vehicle for private equity and venture capital. Dealroom is a global data platform tracking startups and innovation, founded in 2013.",
